{"tid":20000,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過胃酸倒流","createTime":"2016-12-03T06:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T20:08:56.000Z","uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"645024ce017e51f596b88854ab426bdab28383ee","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"食野有時好似吞唔到<br />\n夜晚訓低之後喉嚨同心口痛搞到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過兩日先睇到醫生<br />\n有咩解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5354b250d9f131e045582863680c3a15a32676","tid":20000,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"固定食飯時間，夠訓同固定時間訓教"},{"pid":"41f8e0142b301c42779d3904e6a3527bd80a3a4e","tid":20000,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"訓果陣用啲野墊高個頭會好少少"},{"pid":"f7f2c6b844a4f67269795552b21c931e5984194b","tid":20000,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"臨瞓前1-3個鐘唔好食嘢<br />\n飲奶好似可以舒緩"},{"pid":"40655029481f8dac0ac4b8d7ec681af649f6e3fa","tid":20000,"uid":24144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:22:10.000Z","msg":"小食多餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda0644dac75bce50dd8f7f4c5a390870b72134a","tid":20000,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"可以既話早啲食晚飯，目標八點前食完<br />\nbtw 買定Gaviscon都得"},{"pid":"e686243ce91163accc19a46a0f35deaac5b92814","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>固定食飯時間，夠訓同固定時間訓教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4f590802a7acc005674ccb01657f0da5c496f6","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓果陣用啲野墊高個頭會好少少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今晚試下擺多個枕頭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127af1ff66ff01f3ca9b048d2a0bb9e97e67777e","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臨瞓前1-3個鐘唔好食嘢<br />\n飲奶好似可以舒緩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1652d5b8a7882d6ee81ea875ef8c5c1fe855db","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小食多餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家食野要嚼勁多下慢左成倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805a61fdca123255d6d7c006e4ca759ce140459c","tid":20000,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"一有事我就食嘉胃斯康<br />\n跟住食lomac 同weisen u<br />\n再唔得就食埋pariet 或者rabelprazole"},{"pid":"ba51b36c3c2525c10339d6ea948f56be729ccf88","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以既話早啲食晚飯，目標八點前食完<br />\nbtw 買定Gaviscon都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今晚去屈臣氏買先"},{"pid":"f48dc0643d01305e2ea77e2419c1f2ecf7590ff4","tid":20000,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"食用一粒或兩粒lomac 可減少胃酸<br />\n紓緩胃酸倒流"},{"pid":"6e1c17916d0e49da404b5c8ce2d89202b688f05e","tid":20000,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"074765564e6a1078fea4e2d9f76f5b4b23507034","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食用一粒或兩粒lomac 可減少胃酸<br />\n紓緩胃酸倒流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱search左藥房有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a6aa854ec8cfc11cee03c8a9d17b3245589284","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打胃成日有事？"},{"pid":"4b8e6451a9a34318a79300ea212092e683f4709c","tid":20000,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食用一粒或兩粒lomac 可減少胃酸<br />\n紓緩胃酸倒流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱search左藥房有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我樓下15蚊一排10粒"},{"pid":"c0822fbab1bcffe412018b3b377de0d1c93870ce","tid":20000,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>臨瞓前1-3個鐘唔好食嘢<br />\n飲奶好似可以舒緩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係受害者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時夜瞓去到半夜火燒心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我抄低上面啲藥名先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啊重有碳酸飲品都有壞影響"},{"pid":"f823f80b0bc56eba5f83828bafe7c6f3c17cea50","tid":20000,"uid":7934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"食嘉胃c康其實都會倒流 不過倒流時你會feel到涼涼地，要解決嘅要食減少制造胃酸藥、唔好食太多同太夜食"},{"pid":"bfdaa61d0e32135b938d2d7528011ef2fb9c2ab7","tid":20000,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>臨瞓前1-3個鐘唔好食嘢<br />\n飲奶好似可以舒緩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係受害者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時夜瞓去到半夜火燒心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我抄低上面啲藥名先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啊重有碳酸飲品都有壞影響</blockquote><br />\npariet 好貴, 平均18蚊一粒<br />\n如果唔係好嚴重我都只係食lomac<br />\n最多加粒胃仙u (3蚊粒)<br />\n亦可以加oxema (5毫粒) 但效用不大"},{"pid":"0a876e13200a810818fc7961588da69c656ab87c","tid":20000,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食嘉胃c康其實都會倒流 不過倒流時你會feel到涼涼地，要解決嘅要食減少制造胃酸藥、唔好食太多同太夜食</blockquote><br />\n無錯啦<br />\n同埋嘉胃斯康係倒流緊嗰陣食<br />\n如果無良好習慣的話<br />\n倒慣嘅情況始終係會發生"},{"pid":"36160be83b0cf1132df5eb23b2acfcbfcc957ca9","tid":20000,"uid":50677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食野有時好似吞唔到<br />\n夜晚訓低之後喉嚨同心口痛搞到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過兩日先睇到醫生<br />\n有咩解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我排緊瑪麗醫院等做胃酸倒流手術，8月突然打嚟話有位可以做不過推左再排過。<br />\n而家食緊DEXILANT 60mg 都唔太有效，之前做過2次胃鏡檢查+食道壓力測試同24小時插喉檢查胃酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee40e19b1d847b89323d9f5c9dafb37d216852d","tid":20000,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>臨瞓前1-3個鐘唔好食嘢<br />\n飲奶好似可以舒緩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係受害者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時夜瞓去到半夜火燒心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我抄低上面啲藥名先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啊重有碳酸飲品都有壞影響</blockquote><br />\npariet 好貴, 平均18蚊一粒<br />\n如果唔係好嚴重我都只係食lomac<br />\n最多加粒胃仙u (3蚊粒)<br />\n亦可以加oxema (5毫粒) 但效用不大</blockquote><br />\n其實我好輕微, 都未使睇醫生, 係間中嚟料<br />\n如果嗰個moment, 想食粒最平、最溫和嘅藥舒緩<br />\n即係應該食邊粒?"},{"pid":"3563c759974146e770672c0e420f9adeac4c9a65","tid":20000,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食野有時好似吞唔到<br />\n夜晚訓低之後喉嚨同心口痛搞到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過兩日先睇到醫生<br />\n有咩解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我排緊瑪麗醫院等做胃酸倒流手術，8月突然打嚟話有位可以做不過推左再排過。<br />\n而家食緊DEXILANT 60mg 都唔太有效，之前做過2次胃鏡檢查+食道壓力測試同24小時插喉檢查胃酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打聽落好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前檢查成點？<br />\n我食完上面位巴打推介嘅藥已經好番"},{"pid":"2cb288089e204249f9f2dce66bd15f1d35dc72c2","tid":20000,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"慢慢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}